ed="T" n="0731b08"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0731b08"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000013294">會稽山妙喜寺</placeName><persName key="A009251">印宗</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0731b09"/><persName key="A009251">釋印宗</persName>姓印氏，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName>人也。母<persName key="A021638">劉<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>始娠，隣家<lb
ed="T" n="0731b10"/>咸見一沙門端雅，徐步入<persName key="A009251">印</persName>舍，白<persName key="A021638">劉</persName>曰：「願為<lb
ed="T" n="0731b11"/>子焉。」<ref type="person" target="#A021638">母</ref>夢同此，再三陳讓，不克。<ref type="person" target="#A021639">父</ref>夢有饋<lb
ed="T" n="0731b12"/>栴檀香木童子跪授付<persName key="A021638">劉</persName>。<persName key="A021638">劉</persName>頓厭葷羶，俗<lb
ed="T" n="0731b13"/>間食味隔在脣吻之外。及生而長，從師誦<lb
ed="T" n="0731b14"/>通經典，末最精講者《涅槃經》。<date from-iso="+0670-03-30" key="j19658611966185" to-iso="+0671-02-17">咸亨元年</date>在<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京<lb
ed="T" n="0731b15"/>都</ref>，盛揚道化。<date notBefore-iso="+0674-09-23" key="j19674991968318" notAfter-iso="+0676-12-20">上元中</date>，勅入<placeName key="PL000000023657">大愛敬寺</placeName><ptr target="#n665"/>居，辭<lb
ed="T" n="0731b16"/>不赴，請於<placeName key="PL000000028112">蘄春東山</placeName><persName key="A000237">忍大師</persName>諮受禪法。復<lb
ed="T" n="0731b17"/>於<placeName key="PL000000030482">番禺</placeName>遇<persName key="A001719">慧能禪師</persName><ptr target="#n656"/>，問答之間，深詣玄理。<lb
ed="T" n="0731b18"/>還<ref type="place" target="#PL000000009928">鄉地</ref>，刺史<persName key="A009266">王胄</persName>禮重殊倫，請置戒壇，命<lb
ed="T" n="0731b19"/><persName key="A009251">宗</persName>度人，可數千百。續勅召入內，乃造<persName key="A001428">慈<roleName>氏</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0731b20"/>大像。所著《心要集》，<date from-iso="+0502-04-25" key="j19045262052494" to-iso="+0907-06-09">起梁至唐</date>，天下諸達者<lb
ed="T" n="0731b21"/>語言總錄焉。又奉勅<placeName key="PL000000000197">江東</placeName>諸寺院，<placeName key="PL000000015466">天柱</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000009084">報恩</placeName><ptr target="#n657"/><lb
ed="T" n="0731b22"/>各置戒壇度人。又纂百家諸儒士三教文<lb
ed="T" n="0731b23"/>意表明佛法者，重結集之。手筆逾高，著述<lb
ed="T" n="0731b24"/>流布。至<date key="j19815611981561" when-iso="+0713-03-25"><name>先天</name>二年二月二十一日</date>示終，囑<lb
ed="T" n="0731b25"/>循<persName key="A008870">輪王</persName>法葬之<ptr target="#n658"/>，年八十七。<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName><persName key="A009268">王師乾</persName>立<lb
ed="T" n="0731b26"/>塔銘焉。</p>
